data.description: Absolutely Gorgeous Home!!  This 5 Bedroom, 3.5 Bath Home Is Perfect For Entertaining With Its Large Formal Living And Dining Spaces.  Open Floor Plan But Maintains A Warm Cozy Feel With Lots Of Extras, A Little Family Area, Perfect For Movies And Games By The Warm Fireplace.  Main Level Features, 4 Bedrooms With 2.5 Baths, Living & Dining Areas With Over 3000 Sq Ft.  Also Walk Out The Sliding Doors To Multi Level Deck Overlooking Your In-ground Pool And Patio Area, Absolutely Stunning!  Finished Basement Includes A Complete Living Area, Laundry, Bedroom And Bath.  Would Make A Great In-law Suite Or Rental Opportunity, With Its Private Drive And Parking.  Don't Miss This One, These Do Not Come Along Often!!
